SIMPLE: seljukian
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Seljukian
<hw>Sel*juk"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to <persfn><etsep>Seljuk</etsep></persfn>, a Tartar chief who embraced
Mohammedanism, and began the subjection of Western Asia to that faith
and rule; of or pertaining to the dynasty founded by him, or the empire
maintained by his descendants from the 10th to the 13th century.</def>
<rj><au>J. H. Newman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seljuckian</ent>⟦br⟧
